    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >**人偶镇（Doll Town）**曾是一个以精美手工人偶闻名的繁华村落，如今却在沉默与阴影中腐朽。废弃的工厂、空荡的学校和被遗忘的神龛，是这里仅存的一切——多年以前在此丧生的学生们的记忆，依然在这里徘徊不去。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个短篇故事中，你扮演学生由美（Yumi），她在镇上唯一的便利店找了一份兼职工作，却在无意间步入了一场拒绝被埋葬的噩梦。随着现实与梦境的界限逐渐模糊，由美必须揭开死亡背后的真相、那些受诅咒的玩偶，以及摧毁了整个城镇的可怕爱情故事。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>第三人称探索 穿梭于废弃的街道、学校和工厂，每一个角落都隐藏着秘密……或是威胁。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204320/extras/144505c7ac7d2d569fe8227156b6f3b7.poster.avif?t=1771848202\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204320/extras/144505c7ac7d2d569fe8227156b6f3b7.webm?t=1771848202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204320/extras/144505c7ac7d2d569fe8227156b6f3b7.mp4?t=1771848202\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >氛围感恐怖 将日本乡村的静谧之美与令人窒息的恐惧完美融合，营造出噩梦般的体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204320/extras/3d0028aea378ace0997258d16da117f0.poster.avif?t=1771848202\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204320/extras/3d0028aea378ace0997258d16da117f0.webm?t=1771848202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解开谜团 拼凑出学生们的命运，揭开深藏在小镇核心的凛冽爱情故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204320/extras/e461213f3f057e17961910f1e2305e8a.poster.avif?t=1771848202\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204320/extras/e461213f3f057e17961910f1e2305e8a.webm?t=1771848202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204320/extras/e461213f3f057e17961910f1e2305e8a.mp4?t=1771848202\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >紧张的叙事体验 体验一场慢节奏的沉浸式恐惧，在这里，眼见并不一定为实。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204320/extras/804fe2ae91e6b5c94007bb651e6e420a.poster.avif?t=1771848202\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204320/extras/804fe2ae91e6b5c94007bb651e6e420a.webm?t=1771848202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸式氛围 横向电影级剪辑镜头与环境叙事，带你深入这场悲剧的中心。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204320/extras/2c865447374363034595b6d4e79c2bb7.poster.avif?t=1771848202\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204320/extras/2c865447374363034595b6d4e79c2bb7.webm?t=1771848202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一座建立在人偶之上的小镇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一段以鲜血终结的爱情。 以及一个纠缠不休的诅咒。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到人偶镇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我可以为您做些什么？ 如果您需要将这些文本制作成游戏宣传海报，或者想为主角“由美”润色一些更符合性格的中文对话，请随时告诉我！</p>",
